 Numerous people have been injured in the collision and were attended to at the scene or rushed to hospital. The accident occurred within the vicinity of the Middelburg Provincial Hospital in the location of the rumble strips.  Motorists traveling to or from the R555 (Old Witbank Road) are advised to use Oranje- and Wanderers Streets as a detour. The cleaning of the oil spill is expected to take some time.     Parents frustrated by a lack of space in Middelburg schools Traffic officers to appear in court for corruption #TrafficAlert: Two dead in Kranspoort accidents VIDEO: Two perish after truck jack-knifes • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za